- Are you two having problems?

329
02:11:31,557 --> 02:11:38,156
He's been different
since we've been down here.

330
02:11:38,317 --> 02:11:44,995
- He never got over his father.
- He's not the only one.

331
02:11:45,157 --> 02:11:51,710
