it's like to lose someone you love.

333
02:11:59,237 --> 02:12:03,025
Well, I was very young...
but I know.

334
02:12:07,077 --> 02:12:14,506
- Here's to accidents... fuck 'em.
- Amen.

335
02:12:25,957 --> 02:12:30,633
- He'll bring $500,000 in stud fees.
- Are you kidding?

336
02:12:30,797 --> 02:12:36,986
- Breeding is everything.
- Martha says you've been so weak.

337
02:12:37,157 --> 02:12:40,786
- I hope you don't lose that baby.
- Look, there's old Alice.

338
02:12:40,957 --> 02:12:44,745
I didn't think
she got out much, any more.

339
02:12:44,917 --> 02:12:50,833
- Helen, come and join us.
- Alice is here.

340
02:12:50,997 --> 02:12:55,434
- I don't see anyone.
- I'm going to say hello.

341
02:12:55,597 --> 02:12:59,670
- No, I forbid it.
- Excuse me?

342
02:12:59,837 --> 02:13:06,595
She's just a crazy old woman.
