345
02:13:26,957 --> 02:13:30,632
- What happened? Are you all right?
- Yes.

346
02:13:30,797 --> 02:13:36,110
- You gave me such a scare.
- Why did you yell?

347
02:13:36,277 --> 02:13:41,954
- What the hell happened?
- She walked in front of the horse.

348
02:13:42,117 --> 02:13:45,666
- Are you all right?
- I'm fine.

349
02:13:47,877 --> 02:13:53,315
- Is it near the baby?
- No, it's at the other end.

350
02:13:53,477 --> 02:13:59,473
What's this I hear
about you having the baby at home?

351
