363
02:14:53,757 --> 02:14:56,794
What took you so long?

364
02:14:56,957 --> 02:15:01,872
Go on, spit it out...
you didn't come here for the food.

365
02:15:03,997 --> 02:15:08,673
- Can I ask you a question?
- Please do.

366
02:15:08,837 --> 02:15:14,753
You told me to be careful of Martha.
What did you mean by that?

367
02:15:14,917 --> 02:15:18,068
You mustn't pay any attention to me.

368
02:15:18,237 --> 02:15:21,274
I'm incompetent,
didn't she say that?

369
02:15:21,437 --> 02:15:26,067
And incontinent.
Sort of unreliable at both ends.

370
02:15:26,237 --> 02:15:30,947
Here, girls.
I feed them the whole pharmacy.

371
02:15:31,117 --> 02:15:35,474
Heartburn, ulcers, blood pressure.

372
02:15:35,637 --> 02:15:38,390
They're immune to everything now.

373
02:15:38,557 --> 02:15:41,833
The oldest living Confederates
in America.

374
02:15:41,997 --> 02:15:44,272
There you are, girls.

375
02:15:44,437 --> 02:15:49,272
Here's the thing. I don't
have anybody here to talk to.

376
02:15:49,437 --> 02:15:56,787
Well, I'm kind of busy right now,
but I believe I could fit you in.

377
02:15:56,957 --> 02:16:00,632
Ever since we moved back here...

378
02:16:00,797 --> 02:16:04,756
...Jackson is becoming
more and more distant.

379
02:16:04,917 --> 02:16:08,193
Distant from you, closer to her.

380
02:16:08,357 --> 02:16:12,748
- I think that...
- That you're losing him to Martha.

381
02:16:12,917 --> 02:16:16,193
You're right.
Why don't you say what you mean?

382
02:16:16,357 --> 02:16:21,112
- Maybe I'm just being paranoid.
- She was a stable girl.

383
02:16:21,277 --> 02:16:24,633
- She was?
- Shovelling horse shit.

384
02:16:24,797 --> 02:16:27,994
Not that I hold that against her.

385
02:16:28,157 --> 02:16:31,035
I admire her ambition.

386
02:16:31,197 --> 02:16:36,476
She got herself pregnant.
She got a husband and a son.

387
02:16:36,637 --> 02:16:39,595
And a fine family name.

388
02:16:39,757 --> 02:16:44,706
And now she's breeding herself
a grandson, isn't she?

389
02:16:50,557 --> 02:16:55,426
She never loved my son Jack.
All she ever wanted was that baby.

390
02:16:55,597 --> 02:16:59,033
