she put my son out to pasture.

391
02:16:59,197 --> 02:17:05,067
She took Jackson and poisoned his
mind against his father... and me.

392
02:17:05,237 --> 02:17:11,153
- She'll do the same to you.
- I think she already has.

393
02:17:11,317 --> 02:17:14,832
She made a beautiful widow,
Martha did.

394
02:17:14,997 --> 02:17:18,433
So much more attractive
than a divorced woman.

395
02:17:18,597 --> 02:17:23,990
- Was Jack going to leave Martha?
- Nobody leaves Martha.

396
02:17:24,157 --> 02:17:26,671
Believe me.

397
02:17:28,077 --> 02:17:31,353
You bring Jackson to visit me.

398
02:17:31,517 --> 02:17:35,556
I'll tell him the truth
about his father.

399
02:17:35,717 --> 02:17:38,436
I'm his blood...

400
02:17:38,597 --> 02:17:41,828
...and I love him.

401
02:17:41,997 --> 02:17:46,275
You tell him that.

402
02:18:08,597 --> 02:18:15,469
Dr. Hill, this is Jackson Baring.
Have you seen Helen?

403
02:18:17,277 --> 02:18:22,226
Helen, where have you been?
We've been so worried.

404
02:18:22,397 --> 02:18:27,312
- Am I not to leave the property?
- She just appeared, Dr. Hill.

405
02:18:27,477 --> 02:18:33,791
Just tell us where you're going
so we know where you are.

406
02:18:33,957 --> 02:18:40,715
- Good night, Martha.
- Good night, dear.

407
02:19:07,837 --> 02:19:13,275
She's your grandmother.
She wants to see you. Come with me.

408
02:19:13,437 --> 02:19:19,751
