417
02:20:22,237 --> 02:20:27,231
Cheap is something
you'd know more about than I would.

418
02:20:27,397 --> 02:20:32,391
- Is it cheap here?
- I suppose not.

419
02:20:32,557 --> 02:20:34,912
You suppose right.

420
02:20:35,077 --> 02:20:40,470
